# Naming Conventions

## Files and Directories
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `SocialWall.jsx`)
- Hooks: camelCase with 'use' prefix (e.g., `useAuth.js`)
- Utils: camelCase (e.g., `formatDate.js`)
- Test files: `.test.jsx` or `.spec.jsx`
- Style files: Same name as component with `.css`

## Components
- React Components: PascalCase
- Component Directories: Same as component name

## Variables and Functions
- Variables: camelCase
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
- Functions: camelCase
- React Hooks: use prefix

## CSS Classes
- Tailwind utility classes
- Custom classes: kebab-case
- Component specific: ComponentName-element 
